articles.title: Romania election stunner: Unexpected hard-right candidate now set to reach presidential runoff - POLITICO Europe
articles.description: Ultranationalist Călin Georgescu comes from nowhere to lead center-left PM Marcel Ciolacu and liberal Elena Lasconi in first round.
articles.content:
Georgescu is a university professor and international consultant on sustainable development, who worked for different United Nations organizations for more than a dozen years.
